videos.headline: Jensen knocks down massive Creighton 3
videos.description: Lauren Jensen hits the big 3-pointer to put Creighton ahead of Iowa with less than 15 seconds to play.

videos.headline: Creighton's Jensen had 'nothing to lose' after knocking down 3
videos.description: Lauren Jensen discusses how it felt draining the go-ahead 3 against her former team as the Bluejays upset Iowa.
